atainen's cabinet|Katainen]] <br> [[Alexander Stubb's cabinet|Stubb]]\n}}\n{{Officeholder table\n| order2            = 63\n| image             = Jari_Lindstr\u00f6m.jpg\n| officeholder      = [[Jari Lindstr\u00f6m]]\n| born_year         = 1965\n| died_year         = \n| term_start        = 29 May 2915\n| term_end          = 5 May 2017\n| timeinoffice      = {{age in years and days|2015|5|29|2017|5|5}}\n| alt_party         = True Finns\n| cabinet  = [[Juha Sipil\u00e4's cabinet|Sipil\u00e4]]\n}}\n{{Officeholder table\n| order2            = 64\n| image             = 2017-10_Antti_H\u00e4kk\u00e4nen_1_(cropped).jpg\n| officeholder      = [[Antti H\u00e4kk\u00e4nen]]\n| born_year         = 1985\n| died_year         = \n| term_start        =  5 May 2017\n| term_end          = 6 June 2019\n| timeinoffice      = {{age in years and days|2017|5|5|2019|6|6}}\n| alt_party         = National Coalition Party\n| cabinet  = [[Juha Sipil\u00e4's cabinet|Sipil\u00e4]]\n}}\n{{Officeholder table\n| order2            = (62)\n| image             = Anna-Maja_Henriksson,_2016_\u00c5bo.jpg\n| officeholder      = [[Anna-Maja Henriksson]]\n| born_year         = 1964\n| died_year         = \n| term_start        = 6 June 2019\n| term_end          = ''Incumbent''\n| timeinoffice      = {{age in years and days|2019|6|6}}\n| alt_party         = Swedish People's Party of Finland\n| cabinet  = [[Rinne cabinet|Rinne]] <br> [[Marin Cabinet|Marin]]\n}}\n{{officeholder table end}}\n<ref>{{cite web|url=http://valtioneuvosto.fi/tietoa/historiaa/hallitukset-ja-ministerit/raportti/-/r/v9l/9|title=Finnish Government - Ministers of Justice|publisher=Valtioneuvosto.fi|url-status=live|accessdate=27 December 2017}}</ref>\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n[[Category:Ministers of Justice of Finland|']]\n[[Category:Lists of government ministers of Finland|Justice]]\n", "text_old": "{{Politics of Finland}}\n\nThe '''Minister of Justice''' ({{Lang-fi|oikeusministeri}}, {{Lang-sv|justitieminister}}) is a [[Finnish Government]] ministerial position. The Minister of Justice is in charge of the [[Ministry of Justice (Finland)|Ministry of Justice]].<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://oikeusministerio.fi/en/minister-of-justice|title=Minister of Justice|website=Oikeusministeri\u00f6|language=en-US|access-date=2018-03-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180322015414/http://oikeusministerio.fi/en/minister-of-justice|archive-date=2018-03-22|url-status=dead}}</ref>\n\n[[Finland|Finland's]] incumbent Minister of Justice for the [[Marin Cabinet]] is [[Anna-Maja Henriksson]] of the [[Swedish People's Party of Finland|Swedish People's Party]].<ref>{{cite web |title=T\u00e4ss\u00e4 ovat Marinin hallituksen ministerit \u2013 joukko \u00e4\u00e4nikuningattaria, pikapaluun tekij\u00e4, maailman nuorin p\u00e4\u00e4ministeri |url=https://yle.fi/uutiset/3-11108950 |publisher=Yle |language= Finnish |accessdate=11 December 2019 |date=9 December 2019}}</ref>\n\n==List of Ministers of Justice==\n{{Officeholder table start\n| showorder          = y\n| showimage          = y\n| image_title        = Portrait\n| officeholder_title =  Prices Minister\n| showtermlenght     = y\n| showelection       = n\n| showcoalition      = n\n| showcabinet        = y\n| party_col          = 1\n}}\n{{Officeholder table\n| order2            = 1\n| image             = Onni-Talas-1924.jpg\n| officeholder      = [[Onni Talas]]\n| born_year         = 1877\n| died_year         = 1958\n| term_start        = 27 November 1917\n| term_end          = 27 November 1918\n| timeinoffice      = {{age in years and days|1917|11|27|1918|11|27}}\n| alt_party         = Young Finnish Party\n| cabinet  = [[Pehr Evind Svinhufvud's first senate|Svinhufvud I]] <br> [[Juho Kusti Paasikivi's first senate|Paasikivi I]]\n}}\n{{Officeholder table\n| order2            = 2\n| image             = \n| officeholder      = [[Karl S\u00f6derholm]]\n| born_year         = 1859\n| died_year         = 1948\n| term_start        = 27 November 1918\n| term_end      