Pierre Blackburn]]\n|-\n| style=\"background-color:whitesmoke\" |[[Lac-Saint-Jean\u2014Saguenay|Lac-Saint-Jean]]\n|{{Canadian party colour|CA|PC|background}}|\n|[[Lucien Bouchard]]<br>27,209\n|\n|Bertrand Bouchard<br>5,390\n|\n|Jean Paradis<br>6,348\n|\n|\n|{{Canadian party colour|CA|PC|background}}|\n|[[Lucien Bouchard]]\n|-\n| style=\"background-color:whitesmoke\" |[[Manicouagan (electoral district)|Manicouagan]]\n|{{Canadian party colour|CA|PC|background}}|\n|[[Charles Langlois (politician)|Charles Langlois]]<br>17,126\n|\n|Sylvain Garneau<br>6,355\n|\n|Carol Guay<br>4,008\n|\n|Alan John York (PfC)<br>281\n|{{Canadian party colour|CA|PC|background}}|\n|'''[[Brian Mulroney]]'''\n|-\n| style=\"background-color:whitesmoke\" |[[Roberval (electoral district)|Roberval]]\n|{{Canadian party colour|CA|PC|background}}|\n|[[Beno\u00eet Bouchard]]<br>26,717\n|\n|Martin Cauvier<br>4,219\n|\n|R\u00e9jean Lalancette<br>3,318\n|\n|M\u00e9mile Michel Simard (Rhino) <br>723\n|{{Canadian party colour|CA|PC|background}}|\n|[[Beno\u00eet Bouchard]]\n|}\n\n{{Canada macroriding}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Canadian Federal Election Results In The Cote-Nord And Saguenay}}\n[[Category:Canadian federal election results in Quebec]]\n", "text_old": "{{Unreferenced|date=December 2009}}\n{{Canadian federal election results\n| year1 = [[2019 Canadian federal election|2019]]\n| party1a = BQ\n| seats1a = 4\n| party1b = Conservative\n| seats1b = 1\n| year2 = 2015\n| party2b = NDP\n| seats2b = 1\n| party2d = Conservative\n| seats2d = 2\n| party2c = Liberal\n| seats2c = 1\n| party2a = BQ\n| seats2a = 1\n| year3 = 2011\n| party3a = NDP\n| seats3a = 4\n| party3b = Conservative\n| seats3b = 1\n| year4 = 2008\n| party4a = BQ\n| seats4a = 3\n| party4b = Conservative\n| seats4b = 2\n| year5 = 2006\n| party5a = BQ\n| seats5a = 4\n| party5b = Conservative\n| seats5b = 1\n| year6 = 2004\n| party6a = BQ\n| seats6a = 5\n| year7 = 2000\n| party7a = BQ\n| seats7a = 6\n| party7b = Liberal\n| seats7b = 1\n| year8 = [[1997 